{"tid":364752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反中係香港人既唯一出路","createTime":"2017-08-18T16:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T16:53:15.000Z","uid":34277,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82b39e56aa0aa9d568c315960b77e9ab6d95c66b","tid":364752,"uid":34277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:00:14.000Z","msg":"香港人淨低既出路就係全力反中<br />\n唔只反共，我地仲要反對中華民族意識，反對大一統思想<br />\n咁樣香港人先至能夠從根本省悟中國既禍害"},{"pid":"91a5bf479ed92403280869486a5ed11cc1a40122","tid":364752,"uid":34277,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:01:18.000Z","msg":"同時我地唔應該唔理中國<br />\n反之，我地應該支持中國各地區各省獨立<br />\n中國獨立既地區越多，中共既勢力就越弱，對香港既威脅就越細<br />\n好多地方例如廣東同上海都有排外既情緒<br />\n我地應該好好煽動各地獨立先係"},{"pid":"94f1a68b161ab6718188a861c692e16fcabb46f4","tid":364752,"uid":35236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"不嬲係"},{"pid":"6886c251b671b3c050c8e3754f6e7194f640be5b","tid":364752,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:23:10.000Z","msg":"U don't say"},{"pid":"91ec6ad19092892931d40314ec9879e36da24e9d","tid":364752,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:31:55.000Z","msg":"最弊而家係香港人自己内鬥，你反中對港奸傷害唔大"},{"pid":"870851252a541449835da0592f144e466497c585","tid":364752,"uid":34277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>U don't say</blockquote><br />\n近來五毛假膠充斥時事台<br />\n原諒我開多個阿媽係女人post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bac19b7eb536ad69927e448759ad7f69672e182","tid":364752,"uid":73225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"叫啲港女唔好淘寶慘撚過死呀<br />\n<br />\n再加埋日日周圍都講大陸用語，又手機 又小三 又小鮮肉咁，點會唔同大陸同化"},{"pid":"6ea8751bdf6a48fccdd27657976149c858206155","tid":364752,"uid":110286,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25fc48a351a